{"tid":2445200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣全民救鳳梨卻忘了葡萄！彰化早春葡萄跌價兩成，農民叫苦","createTime":"2021-03-13T12:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T10:28:14.000Z","uid":100680,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6b111c5ee40d427136e74db12c11ece10ca749","tid":2445200,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ccn4iRceo30nSGr6NpmYGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNzkuNzExMTkxMzM1NzQ7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/hrQy1BKSd_x4t1is8lJPPw--~B/aD0xNDc3O3c9MTEwODthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/udn.com/f29f53e16e5b915349e92d480ff85793\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fccn4iRceo30nSGr6NpmYGQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNzkuNzExMTkxMzM1NzQ7Y2Y9d2VicA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhrQy1BKSd_x4t1is8lJPPw--~B%2FaD0xNDc3O3c9MTEwODthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fudn.com%2Ff29f53e16e5b915349e92d480ff85793&h=2f5ef167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全民買鳳梨吃鳳梨救鳳梨，今年溪湖鎮早春葡萄上市，受到南投冬季冷藏葡萄庫存量多，及消費者以鳳梨為主要水果的影響，目前溪湖早春葡萄每盤10公斤的產地批發價為1000元至1100元，比去年1400元下滑約兩成，葡萄農請政府和消費者愛護全體台灣水果，不要獨偏一味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PB4SihFSOEUl_bu9aiuNyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/53PyaYRicNx.or7ywJ.bWg--~B/aD05NjA7dz0xMjgwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/udn.com/eaab95d2bc47767631bdcb40ee92c94d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPB4SihFSOEUl_bu9aiuNyg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F53PyaYRicNx.or7ywJ.bWg--~B%2FaD05NjA7dz0xMjgwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fudn.com%2Feaab95d2bc47767631bdcb40ee92c94d&h=23bce8d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n溪湖鎮公所行政團隊今天前往葡萄園宣傳早春葡萄，鎮長黃瑞珠說，選購葡萄要重視果粉、果粒、果串，霧狀果粒均勻，果粒飽滿，果串完整，每串大約30顆到40顆，溪湖早春葡萄是在溫室栽種，幼果套袋，無農藥殘留，很多農民友善耕種，打開套裝即可食用葡萄，消費者大可安心食用。<br />\n<br />\n農民也是鎮民代表陳興隆說，台灣農業冷藏技術升級，南投縣信義鄉、苗栗縣卓蘭鄉的冬季冷藏葡萄數量相當多，預計最快半個月後賣完，在此之前，台灣葡萄市場供貨量充裕，影響彰化縣溪湖早春葡萄的售價。<br />\n<br />\n陳興隆又說，現在全台搶救鳳梨，政府呼籲全民吃鳳梨，相對排擠其它台灣水果的銷路，葡萄也是台灣水果，種葡萄的農民也是台灣農民，拜託大家不要只吃一種水果，忘記還有很多台灣水果也需要「關愛的眼神」。<br />\n<br />\n溪湖早春葡萄今年產地每盤10公斤批發價1000至1100元，每公斤零售價約80元，去年同期每盤10公斤批發價1400元，換算每公斤零售價140元，葡萄農叫苦不迭，期待南投葡萄冬果賣完，消費者把關愛眼神投射到葡萄等其它台灣水果，半個月後葡萄價格能回升。<br />\n<br />\n彰化是生食葡萄的重要產區，年產值近30億元，彰化葡萄收穫面積約1320公頃，巨峰葡萄占1200公頃，溪湖是巨峰葡萄生產最大產地，種植面積約480公頃，其中約300公頃是溫室早春巨峰葡萄，為彰化縣葡萄產季揭開序幕。"},{"pid":"e3954a0b73b2a505d636350e8bf296109155e71e","tid":2445200,"uid":105207,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:28:36.000Z","msg":"葡萄農葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99dfc907b3aa4e3d148b0972fb01f05fe42dfddc","tid":2445200,"uid":2259,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"9d6b111c5ee40d427136e74db12c11ece10ca749","tid":2445200,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ccn4iRceo30nSGr6NpmYGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNzkuNzExMTkxMzM1NzQ7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/hrQy1BKSd_x4t1is8lJPPw--~B/aD0xNDc3O3c9MTEwODthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/udn.com/f29f53e16e5b915349e92d480ff85793\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fccn4iRceo30nSGr6NpmYGQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNzkuNzExMTkxMzM1NzQ7Y2Y9d2VicA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhrQy1BKSd_x4t1is8lJPPw--~B%2FaD0xNDc3O3c9MTEwODthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fudn.com%2Ff29f53e16e5b915349e92d480ff85793&h=2f5ef167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全民買鳳梨吃鳳梨救鳳梨，今年溪湖鎮早春葡萄上市，受到南投冬季冷藏葡萄庫存量多，及消費者以鳳梨為主要水果的影響，目前溪湖早春葡萄每盤10公斤的產地批發價為1000元至1100元，比去年1400元下滑約兩成，葡萄農請政府和消費者愛護全體台灣水果，不要獨偏一味。<br />\n<br />\n<img sr